::Shadow Wing::

She looked at Lunarpine. She had a solom expression on her face. "This isn't 
living Lunarpine, this is surviving.  Someday we all can settle down. But 
for now, no.  We can't. The Predacons give us little oppertunity to do 
anything at all." She flew next to Lunarpine.
"This isn't a life that lead.  We aren't living. We are surviving. And that 
is all we are doing for the moment.  But if we survive for now, then 
someday, we can live." She turned and took one last look at the Ark.
